\c 5
\s UNehemiya ulaya ukuthi ukucela izibambiso kuyekelwe
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusiba khona ukukhala okukhulu kwabantu labomkabo\x + 5.6. Eks. 3.9. Isa. 5.7.\x* bemelene labafowabo amaJuda\x + Levi 25.35,36. Dute. 15.7.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba kwaba khona abathi: \add Thina\add*, amadodana ethu lamadodakazi ethu sibanengi; ngakho sithethe amabele ukuze sidle siphile.
\v 3 Njalo kwaba khona abathi: Sibambisa amasimu ethu lezivini zethu lezindlu zethu ukuze sithenge amabele endlaleni.
\v 4 Njalo kwaba khona abathi: Seboleke imali yomthelo wenkosi \add ng\add*amasimu ethu lezivini zethu\x + Ezra 4.13.\x*.
\v 5 Khathesi-ke, inyama yethu injengenyama yabafowethu\x + Isa. 58.7. Gen. 29.14.\x*, abantwana bethu banjengabantwana babo; khangela-ke sehlisele phansi amadodana ethu\x + 2 Kho. 4.1.\x* lamadodakazi ethu abe yizigqili\x + Eks. 21.7.\x*; kukhona-ke emadodakazini ethu asehliselwe phansi, njalo isandla sethu kasilamandla, ngoba abanye balamasimu ethu lezivini zethu.
\p
\v 6 Ngathukuthela kakhulu nxa ngisizwa ukukhala kwabo lalamazwi.
\v 7 Inhliziyo yami isicabangile phakathi kwami, ngasengilwisana lezikhulu lababusi, ngathi kubo: Libhadalisa inzuzo, ngulowo kumfowabo. Ngabamisela umhlangano omkhulu\x + Eks. 22.25.\x*.
\v 8 Ngasengisithi kibo: Thina ngamandla akithi sihlenge abafowethu amaJuda ababethengiswe ezizweni; lani selizathengisa abafowethu, kumbe bazathengiswa kithi yini? Basebethula, kabatholanga mpendulo\x + Levi 25.48,49.\x*.
\v 9 Ngasengisithi: Into eliyenzayo kayilunganga. Belingehambe yini ngokwesaba uNkulunkulu wethu\x + 5.15. Levi 25.17,36,43.\x* ngenxa yehlazo lezizwe, izitha zethu\x + 4.4. 2 Sam. 12.14.\x*?
\v 10 Ngitsho lami, abafowethu, lenceku zami, besikweledisa imali lamabele. Asiyekeleni inzuzo lezi.
\v 11 Ake libabuyisele lalamuhla amasimu abo, izivini zabo, izihlahla zabo zemihlwathi, lezindlu zabo, lokwekhulu kwemali lokwamabele lokwewayini elitsha lokwamafutha elibabhadalisa khona.
\v 12 Basebesithi: Sizabuyisela, singabizi lutho kubo. Sizakwenza njalo njengokutsho kwakho. Ngasengibiza abapristi, ngabafungisa\x + Ezra 10.5.\x* ukuthi benze njengalelilizwi\x + Jer. 34.8,9.\x*.
\v 13 Ngasengithintitha ithangazi lami\x + Seb. 18.6.\x* ngathi: Ngokunjalo uNkulunkulu kathintithe wonke umuntu asuke endlini yakhe\x + Eks. 14.27.\x* lemsebenzini wakhe ongasoze amise lelilizwi\x + Isa. 45.14.\x*; langokunjalo kathintithwe angabi lalutho. Lebandla lonke lathi: Ameni. Bayidumisa iN\nd kosi\nd*. Abantu basebesenza njengalelilizwi\x + 8.6. 1 Kor. 14.16. Nani 5.22.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Futhi kusukela ngosuku angilaya ngalo ukuthi ngibe ngumbusi wabo elizweni lakoJuda\x + 1 Kho. 10.15.\x*, kusukela emnyakeni wamatshumi amabili\x + 2. 1.\x* kuze kube semnyakeni wamatshumi amathathu lambili kaAthakisekisi inkosi\x + 13.6.\x*, iminyaka elitshumi lambili, mina labafowethu kasidlanga isinkwa\x + 5.18. 2 Thes. 3.8.\x* sombusi\x + 1 Kho. 10.15.\x*.
\v 15 Kodwa ababusi bamandulo ababengaphambi kwami babathwalisa nzima abantu, bethatha kibo isinkwa lewayini, emva kwalokhu \w amashekeli\w** esiliva angamatshumi amane; lenceku zabo zabusa nzima phezu kwabantu\x + 1 Kho. 10.15.\x*; kodwa mina kangenzanga njalo ngenxa yokwesaba uNkulunkulu\x + 5.9.\x*.
\v 16 Phezu kwalokho-ke ngaqina emsebenzini walumduli, njalo kasithenganga insimu; lenceku zami zonke zabuthana lapho emsebenzini.
\v 17 Lamadoda alikhulu lamatshumi amahlanu kumaJuda lakubabusi, lalabo abeza kithi bevela ezizweni ezisihanqileyo, babesetafuleni lami\x + 2 Sam. 9.10. 1 Kho. 18.19.\x*.
\v 18 Lalokhu okwakulungiselwe usuku olulodwa kwakuyinkabi eyodwa, izimvu ezikhethiweyo eziyisithupha, lezinyoni zazilungiselwe mina, njalo phakathi kwensuku ezilitshumi okwalo lonke iwayini ngobunengi\x + 1 Kho. 4.22.\x*. Langalokhu kangizanga ngidinge isinkwa\x + 5.14,15.\x* sombusi\x + 1 Kho. 10.15.\x*, ngoba ubugqili babunzima phezu kwalababantu.
\v 19 Ngikhumbule, Nkulunkulu wami, ngokuhle, konke engikwenzele lababantu\x + 13.14,22,31. 2 Kho. 20.3.\x*.